<div>
<h2>Upload Farmer Data</h2>
<h4>Step 1: Create a valid upload file using this <a href="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/egranary-uploads/eGranary_Farmer_Upload_Template.xlsx">template file</a></h4>
<h4>Step 2: Click the button below and upload the file</h4>
<h4>Step 3: Check your email for a confirmation that the upload has completed in a few minutes</h4>

<%= form_tag({action: :upload_data}, :class => 'directUpload', data: { 'form-data' => (@s3_direct_post.fields), 'url' => @s3_direct_post.url, 'host' => URI.parse(@s3_direct_post.url).host }) do %>
  <%= file_field_tag :farmer_data %>
<% end %>

</div>